bug.short_desc: Default label theme for iOS is not readable

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1143 mobile tutorial screenshot
Open the attached example from the mobile tutorial. The tweet which is just a default label is not readable (gray on gray). We should improve the theme (change the text color or the background).
Another way: Put a container around the label. So we just have to change the mobile tutorial.

Solved with implementation of GroupBox. Updated Mobile Showcase, too.
